content.title: AIRBEAT ONE FESTIVAL
Dosenmatrosen - Vorbestellungen enden bald!
content.text:
🚨 Letzte Chance! 🚨

Bestelle deine Getränke für das Airbeat One Festival bei Dosenmatrosen.de vor! 🎉

Nur noch bis zum 05.07. hast du die Möglichkeit, dir deine kalten Drinks bequem online bei Dosenmatrosen.de zu bestellen und auf das Festivalgelände liefern zu lassen. 🥤❄️

Verpasse nicht die Gelegenheit – jetzt vorbestellen und entspannt feiern! 🍻

https://www.dosenmatrosen.de/airbeat

content.title: AIRBEAT ONE Festival 2024 Upgrades! 🌟
content.text: Mainstage & Hardstyle Area bigger than ever, new Classic Area and Delay Tower at the Mainstage. New food trucks & additional food area near Nord Camping. Also: more toilets & showers + new positioning and better visibility of the sanitary facilities. The new P4 parking lot offers shorter distances directly at the Special and Nord Camping. With the new fiber optic connection, the cell phone network is strengthened and our water network is also expanded.

content.title: LATEST NEWS
content.text:
Dear Traveler,

from now on you can load money onto your festival wristband. You should also use the last chance to book our camping add-ons. To make your journey easier, we recommend our bus tours. Drinks, ice cubes and more will be provided by the Dosenmatrosen again this year. And so that you can start the festival in an organized way, we have information about the timetable and the maps of the site here. You can find all the information on these topics in the newsletter right here: 

https://us14.campaign-archive.com/?e=[UNIQID]&u=2016f05b405e531cd4f6fbdf4&id=ba8e712597

Your AIRBEAT ONE Team

content.title: Cashless TopUp Portal open
content.text:
From now on the TopUp Portal is open and you can top up money on your festival wristband!
Your credit will be automatically transferred to your festival wristband. Your advantages are: you save the queuing at a TopUp station at the festival and can enjoy the festival relaxed from the beginning. With your wristband you can pay for food, drinks and merchandise at AIRBEAT ONE Festival 2024. 

 

And here is a short instruction to top up money:
1. Login with account / registration
2. Create wallet (you can add 1 ticket per wallet)
3. select ticket provider & enter barcode
4. choose "go to store" & select specific amount of money
5. go to checkout & select desired payment method

You can find the portal here: https://airbeatone2024.eventportal.io

content.title: Travel survey
content.text:
📢🚗 Take part in our travel survey and, with a bit of luck, win great prizes! Your opinion counts - help us to make the AIRBEAT ONE Festival even better. Take part now and take your chance!

Click here for the survey: https://forms.gle/dKMQXMpaPFi99BSW8 

You can win the following:
10x 2 Funflat (ticket for unlimited use of the rides on site)
5x 2 Main 1 camping tickets
2x 2 VIP camping tickets
5x 50€ cashless credit
2x 2 3 DAY VIP Gold

content.title: FULL LINE-UP AIRBEAT ONE FESTIVAL 2024
content.text:
Dear Traveler,

welcome to AIRBEAT ONE Festival 2024, the biggest electronic music festival in Germany! This year, we are proud to present a line-up that is second to none. You can expect amazing DJs from all corners of the world to thrill you on seven different stages.

From international headliners to up-and-coming talent, experience the crème de la crème of the electronic music scene alongside 225,000 like-minded guests. The stages will present themselves true to the motto France and offer you the best sounds. Our line-up reflects the diversity of electronic music - hard-hitting bass, euphoric EDM, deep house, techno and psytrance beats will transport you to a musical paradise.

Don't miss out on this unique festival. Get your tickets and be ready to be part of a legendary musical spectacle that you will remember for a long time to come.

Your AIRBEAT ONE Team

content.title: AFTERMOVIE AIRBEAT ONE FESTIVAL 2023
content.text:
Finally – Are you ready to relive the best weekend of the year?!

The aftermovie of AIRBEAT ONE Festival 2023 is here and it brings back the memories of this unforgettable event! Let’s revel in those moments together and ignite the anticipation for next year even more!

For all those who missed the festival or are just longingly looking for the highlights, the aftermovie offers a refreshing way to relive this unique atmosphere. The energy of the crowd in front of the Mainstage literally vibrates through the screen. The breathtaking visuals immediately send you into a trance and awaken pure ecstasy.

The camera moves over huge dance floors with thousands of dancing festival visitors – pure goosebumps! You can literally feel this irresistible beat spreading through your entire body. The interplay of light effects and music makes every fiber of our being pulsate.

This short glimpse into the past AIRBEAT ONE Festival makes you want more – to be part of such a magical experience; surrounded by like-minded people full of joy of life and the desire for musical ecstasy.

So get inspired by the new aftermovie and set your anticipation free for next year! Tickets are already available – be there for the next big highlight of our time: the AIRBEAT ONE Festival 2024!

content.title: ADD AIRBEAT ONE TO YOUR BUCKET LIST!
content.text:
The pyro and laser shows were INSANE! 🔥🎉 We were blown away by the incredible displays and couldn't get enough. 

If you haven't experienced a pyro or laser show yet, you NEED to add the AirbeatOne Festival to your bucket list for next year. 🙌

AIRBEAT ONE Festival
10.-14. July 2024
Neustadt-Glewe, Germany
Tickets: here!
